import django_filters
from django_filters import rest_framework as filters
from ..models import Career


class CareerFilter(filters.FilterSet):
    experience_level = filters.CharFilter(field_name='experience_level__level_name', lookup_expr='icontains')
    job_title = filters.CharFilter(field_name='title', lookup_expr='icontains')
    toggle = filters.BooleanFilter(field_name='is_show')
    auto_expiration = filters.BooleanFilter(field_name='enable_auto_expiration')

    class Meta:
        model = Career
        fields = ['experience_level', 'job_title', 'toggle', 'auto_expiration']
